  characterName: Dr. Sturgeon
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3cadb61783a8ad44abb478954be17e5d, type: 3}
  lines:
  - Look at you big boy.
  - Your persistence is making me THROB!
  - If only there was something I could do to reward your good behaviour.
  - Oh, I have an idea. Let me tell you a secret.
  - Myself and Perch are actually brothers.
  - And we have a beautiful son together.
  - Although he does not live up here on the surface with us anymore.
  - No.
  - He definitely doesn't.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
